    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事开始时，你在一个神秘的世界醒来，记忆尽失，旅程由此展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首先，你需要学会生存 — 采集资源，制作物品，建造营地。你可以选择独自求生，也可以招募村民，建立一个繁荣的部落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你探索荒野时，将会遭遇各种魔物。打造装备、学习魔法，然后击败它们！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上广袤的旅途，寻找线索，解开你漂泊至此的谜团。或者，你也可以悠然躺平，静享田园生活。一切由你决定！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心玩法亮点</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >钓鱼</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326670/extras/a337fa4a9903b0538f801ca1b6221d9b.avif?t=1771984071\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326670/extras_big/a337fa4a9903b0538f801ca1b6221d9b.avif?t=1771984071 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打猎与采集资源</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326670/extras/92f8a6a0dd2f41a325a3079b2bc83774.avif?t=1771984071\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326670/extras_big/92f8a6a0dd2f41a325a3079b2bc83774.avif?t=1771984071 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制作与建造</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326670/extras/af81e5b695952b2114d14b66aab0da73.avif?t=1771984071\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326670/extras_big/af81e5b695952b2114d14b66aab0da73.avif?t=1771984071 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >烹饪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326670/extras/93fba0f9c1e47347ca0eff33e167e08b.avif?t=1771984071\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326670/e